      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAROS DREAM (2) struggled to get involved last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by 3 lengths at this track (17.62) beating SHINBONER ABBY in a Novice race on March 9. Has ability and is a key runner. NITRO'S IZZY (1) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (17.79) at this track. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Deserves a win and gets her chance. SPARE ME (4) collided with another runner and finished a well held 13 lengths seventh (18.29) last time in a Novice race at this track over 300m. Can measure up this time. ZATARA ACE (3) was below best last time at this track (18.31) in a Novice race, finishing a 15 length sixth. Already a winner from this draw.",
